{"id":285630,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/global-voices-阿根廷新教宗豪尔赫．伯格里奥/","date":"2013-03-24T02:45:30Z","modified":"2017-02-03T22:23:22Z","title":"Global Voices | 阿根廷新教宗豪尔赫．伯格里奥","content":"<p><p>天主教会新任教宗由阿根廷耶稣会枢机主教<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jorge_Bergoglio\">豪尔赫．马里奥．伯格里奥</a>出任。自 2013 年三月十三日起伯格里奥成为教宗方济。</p>\n<p>网友们迅速对史上第一次由拉丁美洲出身的阿根廷人领导天主教会做出反应。</p>\n<p>来自布宜诺斯艾利斯的 Rodrigo Hernán Torres（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/RodrigoH_Torre/\">@RodrigoH_Torre</a>）写道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/RodrigoH_Torre/status/311927572864835584\">@RodrigoH_Torre</a>：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Bergoglio&#038;src=hash\">#伯格里奥</a>是我们的教宗。恭喜！在这个历史时刻，祝他面对这个新的挑战和新的道路一切顺利。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Card._Jorge_Bergoglio_SJ,_2008.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-400077\" alt=\"Jorge Bergoglio, image from Wikimedia Commons\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/505px-Card._Jorge_Bergoglio_SJ_2008-252x300.jpg\" width=\"252\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>豪尔赫．伯格里奥。照片来自维基共享资源。</p>\n</div>\n<p>这个消息让许多网友联想起足球，比如 Aaron Zamost（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/zamosta/\">@zamosta</a>）提到起马拉度纳的“上帝之手”：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/zamosta/status/311920019988697088\">@zamosta</a>：知晓上帝之手的阿根廷人中，教宗方济只是第二有名的。<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://t.co/6QH7hMtvzL\">http://bit.ly/KpI47u</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>美国电视主持人 Piers Morgan（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/piersmorgan\">@piersmorgan</a>）也对阿根廷足球有意见：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/piersmorgan/status/311918771692519426\">@piersmorgan</a>：阿根廷现在有着地球上最佳天主教徒和最佳足球员。<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Bergoglio&#038;src=hash\">#Bergoglio</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Messi&#038;src=hash\">#Messi</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Caren Kalafatich（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/CarenKalafatich/\">@CarenKalafatich</a>）的发言比较严肃：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/CarenKalafatich/status/311927547342487552\">@CarenKalafatich</a>：我们来自阿根廷，而这是我们的本质：我们因为教宗是阿根廷人而庆贺，而忽略 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Bergoglio&#038;src=hash\">#伯格里奥</a> 这个人和他的保守主义。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>有些网友质疑教宗跟阿根廷 1976-1983 年独裁统治的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://articles.latimes.com/2005/apr/17/world/fg-cardinal17\">关联</a>，例如 Guillermo Prein（<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/GuillermoPrein/\">@GuillermoPrein</a>）：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/GuillermoPrein/status/311930384139042818\">@GuillermoPrein</a>：尽管和独裁统治牵扯不清以及包庇像是 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.buenosairesherald.com/BreakingNews/View/3501\">Grassi</a> 的恋童案，<a rel=\"nofollow\" dir=\"ltr\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Bergoglio&#038;src=hash\">#伯格里奥</a>枢机主教仍被选为教宗。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>我们将为您带来报导阿根廷和拉丁美洲人民对此事的反应，敬请继续关注。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/silvia-vinas/\" title=\"文章导读 Silvia Viñas\">Silvia Viñas</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/hllee/\" title=\"文章导读 Hsu-Lei Lee\">Hsu-Lei Lee</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/03/13/new-pope-jorge-bergoglio-is-argentinian/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/03/24/12336/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%96%B0%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%B0%94%E8%B5%AB%EF%BC%8E%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E5%A5%A5&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F24%2F12336%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F24%2F12336%2F&#038;desc=%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%96%B0%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%B0%94%E8%B5%AB%EF%BC%8E%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E5%A5%A5\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/\" onclick=\"javascript:var js=document.createElement (\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F24%2F12336%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F24%2F12336%2F&#038;text=%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%96%B0%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%B0%94%E8%B5%AB%EF%BC%8E%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E5%A5%A5&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2013%2F03%2F24%2F12336%2F&#038;title=%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E6%96%B0%E6%95%99%E5%AE%97%E8%B1%AA%E5%B0%94%E8%B5%AB%EF%BC%8E%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8C%E5%A5%A5\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"